views.text: An irresistible tale of exasperation at first sight! Caroline is a young, single interior designer living in San Francisco. She moves into an apartment that seems perfect, only to be awakened nightly by her neighbor, Simon aka "Wallbanger" and his sexual escapades. His enjoyment only furthers her frustration that she's lost her orgasm and can't seem to get it back. The tension between them is as thick as the walls are thin and suddenly, Caroline finds that she may have discovered a whole new definition of neighborly.
